<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    {{ block "header" . }} {{ end }}
    {{ block "conf_seo" . }} {{ end }}
  </head>
<body>
{{ block "conf_nav" .Conf }} {{ end }}
<section id="intro" class="lg:mb-20 lg:pb-20">
 <div class="relative">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="relative z-10 pt-14 lg:w-full lg:max-w-2xl">
        <svg class="absolute inset-y-0 right-8 hidden h-full w-80 translate-x-1/2 transform fill-white lg:block" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <polygon points="0,0 90,0 50,100 0,100" />
        </svg>

        <div class="relative px-6 pt-12 pb-12 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-12 lg:px-8 lg:pt-12 lg:pb-24 lg:pr-0">
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-xl">
            <div class="hidden sm:mb-10 sm:flex">
              <div class="relative rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-500 ring-1 ring-gray-900/10 hover:ring-gray-900/20">
                Showcase at the frontier of bitcoin development.<a href="/sponsor" target="_blank" class="whitespace-nowrap font-semibold riga-color"><span class="absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true"></span>Become a Sponsor<span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl"><span class="font-bitcoin">bitcoin++</span> is going private</h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">Join us in Riga next summer and peer into the frontier of Bitcoin privacy</p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">Riga, Latvia | National Library of Riga | 7+8 August 2025</p>
            <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-x-6">
              <a href="#tickets" class="rounded-md px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 riga">Get Your All Conf Pass</a>
            </div>
            {{ template "conf_countdown" .Conf }}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-30 mt-6 sm:mt-8 lg:absolute lg:inset-x-0 lg:bottom-0 lg:mt-0 lg:translate-y-[calc(50%+20px)]">
      {{ template "sponsor_banner" . }}
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:w-1/2">
      <picture>
        <source srcset="/static/img/riga/leading.avif" type="image/avif"/>
        <img 
          class="aspect-[3/2] object-cover lg:aspect-auto lg:h-full w-full" 
          src="/static/img/riga/leading-200.png" 
          loading="lazy"
          srcset="
          /static/img/riga/leading-200.png 320w,
          /static/img/riga/leading-400.png 800w,
          /static/img/riga/leading-800.png 1200w
          "
      alt="">
      </picture>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="about">
  <div class="overflow-hidden bg-white pt-14 pb-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:flex lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white py-10 sm:py-10">
        <h2 class="text-center mt-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Why privacy?</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">Transacting privately is a cornerstone of freedom from tyranny and control. Bitcoin is an important tool at the forefront of freedom to transact peer to peer. It's transparency and auditability however are often at odds with the goal of perserving an individual's right to privacy. Join us in Riga this coming August 7+8 for a deep dive into the forefront of privacy and peer to peer exchange, both on-chain and off.</p>
        <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 overflow-hidden lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-4 mt-12">
          <div>
            <time datetime="2025-01" class="flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 riga-color">
            Privacy + Public Good
          </div>
          <div>
            <time datetime="2021-12" class="flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 riga-color">
            Freedom to Transact
          </div>
          <div>
            <time datetime="2022-02" class="flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 riga-color">
            Censorship Resistance
          </div>
          <div>
            <time datetime="2022-12" class="flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 riga-color">
            Open Source 
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="venue">
<div class="overflow-hidden bg-white pt-14 pb-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:flex lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-12 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:min-w-full lg:max-w-none lg:flex-none lg:gap-y-8">
      <div class="lg:col-end-1 lg:w-full lg:max-w-lg lg:pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Destination: Riga, Latvia</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600">Experience the Baltics, catch some Honeybadgers, and work on your opsec</p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600"><span class="font-bitcoin">bitcoin++</span> is excited to be headed to Riga, Latvia ahead of the Baltic Honeybadger conference in 2025.</p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex">
          <a href="#tickets" class="rounded-md px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 riga">Get Your All Access Pass<span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-end gap-6 sm:gap-8 lg:contents">
        <div class="w-0 flex-auto lg:ml-auto lg:w-auto lg:flex-none lg:self-end">
          <img src="/static/img/riga/courtyard.jpg" alt="" class="aspect-[7/5] w-[37rem] max-w-none rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="contents lg:col-span-2 lg:col-end-2 lg:ml-auto lg:flex lg:w-[37rem] lg:items-start lg:justify-end lg:gap-x-8">
          <div class="order-first flex w-64 flex-none justify-end self-end lg:w-auto">
            <img src="/static/img/riga/bitcoin_riga.webp" alt="" class="aspect-[4/3] w-[24rem] max-w-none flex-none rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="flex w-96 flex-auto justify-end lg:w-auto lg:flex-none">
            <img src="/static/img/riga/riga_plaza.jpg" alt="" class="aspect-[7/5] w-[37rem] max-w-none flex-none rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="hidden sm:block sm:w-0 sm:flex-auto lg:w-auto lg:flex-none">
            <img src="/static/img/riga/baltic.webp" alt="" class="aspect-[4/3] w-[24rem] max-w-none rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 object-cover">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
